    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Cheated of Future, Iraqi Graduates Want to Flee'' (front page, June 5):</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''Cheated of Future, Iraqi Graduates Want to Flee'' (front page, June 5):</p>
        <p>The future of Iraq is indeed dismal if Iraq's newest college graduates leave, rather than staying, working and fighting to help make Iraq a better country.</p>
        <p>How do we tell our young soldiers that they should risk their lives for a cause that their Iraqi contemporaries are abandoning?</p>
        <p>John V. Kjellman  Henniker, N.H., June 5, 2007</p>
      </block>
